      <div class="container">
         <!-- Example row of columns -->
         <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-4">
               <h2>Why jquery.country</h2>
               <p>The jquery.country help you let your business model cleaner, avoiding unnecessary creation of entities, tables and relationships that obfuscate the main purpose of your software.</p>
			   <p>Help save resources in the database, all information about regions are stored in minified json files.</p>
			   <p>Saves development time that is usually wasted to organize and assemble a database of regional information.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
               <h2>For who?</h2>
               <p>For any web developer that needs a simple solution to collect location information of their users.</p>
			   <p>Is highly recommended for software that does not require that the location information be stored in a relational database.</p>
			   <p>If your software does not have business rules related to region location, probably this plugin fits for you.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
               <h2>Contribute</h2>
               <p>The plugin is an open-source project with the goal of supporting all regions of the globe.</p>
			   <p>The plugin is in development phase, its beta version was delivered with only the regions of Brazil.</p>
			   <p>If you need support for other regions please contact us and help us collect information.</p>
            </div>
